elements.expression:
filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT dna.keyword as Facet, count(dna.keyword) as Vol FROM \"dataspects*\" GROUP BY dna.keyword"
| table paginate=false
| render

filters
| demodata
| markdown "### dataspects Monitoring"
| render

filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT dna.keyword as Facet, count(dna.keyword) as Vol FROM \"dataspects*\" WHERE dna.keyword IN('Templates having METADATA template', 'EntityType category members') GROUP BY dna.keyword"
| pointseries x="Vol" y="Facet" color="project"
| plot defaultStyle={seriesStyle bars=0.75 horizontalBars=true} legend=false xaxis=true seriesStyle={seriesStyle} 
  palette={palette "#01A4A4" "#CC6666" "#D0D102" "#616161" "#00A1CB" "#32742C" "#F18D05" "#113F8C" "#61AE24" "#D70060" gradient=false}
| render

filters
| demodata
| markdown "These must all be equal in pairs." 
  font={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=14 align="left" color="#fd7643" weight="normal" underline=false italic=true}
| render

filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT pagename AS EntityType FROM \"dataspects*\" Where dna.keyword = 'EntityType category members'"
| table paginate=true perPage=25 showHeader=true
| render
